snippet.title: A500 Turrican - Intro
snippet.description:
Having and Amiga and never playing this is criminal. The first of one of the most famous games by Factor 5 ever made, brought arcade quality platform shooting action to my home. Legendary OST by childhood reference, Chris Hüelsbeck, that used is own TMFX format to make the Amiga output 7* sound channels, instead of the regular 4.

*UPDATE: It has been pointed out to me that only "Turrican II" uses 7 channels, "Turrican" uses TMFX but all songs are 4 channel only.
